    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Jewish Tipping Point</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Rabbi Jeffrey L Falick letter on Samuel G Freedman's August 13 article opposes liberal Jews in Beachwood, Ohio, for using legal process as form of 'payback' against Orthodox communities (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>In their resentment over what they perceive to be Orthodox intolerance, many liberal Jews have done the unthinkable: they have utilized the legal process as a form of ''payback'' to Orthodox communities. This is an abuse of the very system that we all depend upon for our freedom of worship and freedom of assembly.</p>
        <p>Rabbi Jeffrey L. Falick  Miami</p>
      </block>
